id: pm-25se
title: "GH-209 follow-up: OTEL span export keeps the CLI alive ~10s (and can exit 13) when the traces endpoint is unreachable"
description: ""
type: Issue
status: in_progress
priority: 1
tags: []
created_at: "2026-06-14T05:50:40.983Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-14T06:01:27.397Z"
